Titolo: Space Spartans

Anno: 1982

Descrizione: Space Spartans is a space combat simulator video game released for Intellivision, initially programmed by Brian Dougherty, and completed by William C. Fisher and Steve Roney. It is first game which supported the Intellivoice voice synthesis module. Space Spartans is heavily based on Star Raiders, a game released in 1979 for the Atari 8-bit family.